    <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
    <p>
      This report covers the operational and financial performance of the technological division for the first quarter of 2026. Despite challenging market conditions, we have seen robust growth across our core service APIs and cloud platforms.
    </p>
    <p>
      The introduction of the new <em>goxml2pdf</em> service line has shown promising early adoption rates among our enterprise clients, processing over 50,000 documents in its first month of beta availability.
    </p>

    <h2>Financial Performance</h2>
    <p>
      Overall revenue for the quarter exceeded targets by 4.2%, driven primarily by increased API usage from the financial sector.
    </p>
    
